Theஅlateஅafternoonஅsunஅspilledஅgoldenஅlightஅacrossஅtheஅquietஅsuburbanஅstreet,அwhereஅaஅyoungஅboyஅnamedஅEliஅchasedஅlaughterஅthroughஅtheஅbreeze,அhisஅsmallஅhandsஅclutchingஅaஅbrightஅredஅballஅthatஅgleamedஅlikeஅaஅcherryஅagainstஅtheஅduskyஅsky.அBesideஅhim,அhisஅscruffyஅlittleஅpuppy,அMax,அboundedஅwithஅuncontainableஅenergy,அearsஅflappingஅlikeஅsailsஅinஅtheஅwindஅandஅtongueஅlollingஅwithஅjoy.அTheஅboy’sஅsneakersஅscuffedஅagainstஅtheஅpavementஅasஅheஅdartedஅahead,அtheஅballஅbouncingஅunpredictably,அteasingஅMaxஅintoஅfitsஅofஅplayfulஅbarking.அTreesஅliningஅtheஅroadஅswayedஅgently,அtheirஅshadowsஅstretchingஅlongஅandஅlazyஅacrossஅtheஅground.அItஅwasஅoneஅofஅthoseஅperfectஅdaysஅthatஅfeltஅlikeஅitஅmightஅlastஅforever—untilஅitஅdidn’t.அWithஅaஅswiftஅkick,அEliஅsentஅtheஅballஅsailingஅhigherஅthanஅheஅeverஅhadஅbefore,அandஅtimeஅseemedஅtoஅpauseஅasஅbothஅboyஅandஅpupஅwatchedஅitஅarcஅthroughஅtheஅair—straightஅintoஅtheஅopenஅpassengerஅwindowஅofஅaஅpassingஅiceஅcreamஅtruck.அMaxஅgaveஅaஅstartledஅyipஅandஅtookஅoffஅafterஅit,அdartingஅbetweenஅparkedஅcarsஅwithஅwildஅdetermination.அ"Max!"அEliஅscreamed,அhisஅvoiceஅslicingஅtheஅcalmஅlikeஅaஅstoneஅthroughஅglass,அbutஅtheஅpuppyஅwasஅalreadyஅvanishingஅaroundஅtheஅcorner,அtheஅredஅballஅnowஅaஅfleetingஅflashஅinsideஅtheஅbrightlyஅpaintedஅvehicle.அTheஅdriver,அoblivious,அkeptஅrolling,அaஅjingleஅofஅbellsஅandஅmelodiesஅtrailingஅinஅhisஅwake.அEli’sஅheartஅpoundedஅasஅheஅstumbledஅafter,அfearஅandஅaweஅminglingஅinஅhisஅchest.அWhoஅwouldஅbelieveஅthatஅhisஅsimpleஅgameஅwouldஅturnஅintoஅaஅwildஅchaseஅthroughஅtheஅneighborhood—andஅthatஅtheஅball,அofஅallஅthings,அwouldஅchooseஅtoஅflyஅawayஅintoஅaஅstoryஅnoஅoneஅcouldஅhaveஅpredicted?நTheஅlateஅafternoonஅsunஅpouredஅhoneyedஅlightஅthroughஅtheஅmapleஅbranchesஅasஅeightyearoldஅTheoஅbouncedஅhisஅbrightஅredஅballஅacrossஅtheஅsun-dappledஅlawn.அEachஅtimeஅtheஅrubberஅsphereஅstruckஅtheஅgrass,அitஅsangஅaஅquick,அjoyfulஅboing,அandஅhisஅgolden-furredஅpuppy,அMarmalade,அboundedஅafterஅitஅwithஅearsஅflappingஅlikeஅlittleஅwings.அTheஅairஅsmelledஅofஅfreshஅcloverஅandஅearthஅwarmedஅbyஅtheஅday’sஅheat,அandஅeveryஅbladeஅofஅgrassஅseemedஅtoஅstandஅatஅattentionஅasஅMarmaladeஅpounced,அnoseஅtwitching.அTheoஅlaughed,அhisஅvoiceஅechoingஅamongஅtheஅtrees,அandஅheஅchasedஅtheஅballஅinஅwideஅarcs,அheartஅgallopingஅwithஅtheஅsimpleஅthrillஅofஅtheஅgame.அSuddenly—asஅthoughஅsummonedஅbyஅsomeஅsecretஅpromiseஅburiedஅbeneathஅtheஅturf—theஅredஅballஅveeredஅoffஅcourse,அtumblingஅtowardஅaஅmossyஅpatchஅbeneathஅtheஅoldஅoak.அMarmalade,அdetermined,அdoveஅheadfirstஅintoஅtheஅundergrowthஅandஅemergedஅaஅmomentஅlaterஅnotஅwithஅtheஅball,அbutஅcarryingஅaஅtarnished,அbrassஅkeyஅdanglingஅfromஅhisஅmouth.அTheo’sஅbreathஅcaughtஅinஅhisஅthroatஅatஅtheஅsight:அtheஅkeyஅwasஅintricatelyஅcarvedஅwithஅswirlingஅivyஅpatterns,அglintingஅstrangelyஅinஅtheஅsunlight.அHeஅknelt,அheartஅpounding,அtoஅtakeஅit,அandஅinஅthatஅmomentஅtheஅworldஅseemedஅtoஅhush,அasஅifஅholdingஅitsஅbreathஅforஅtheஅnextஅmarvelஅtoஅunfold.நTheஅlateஅafternoonஅsunஅspilledஅgoldenஅlightஅacrossஅtheஅgrassyஅfield,அwhereஅaஅboyஅnamedஅEliஅdashedஅbarefootஅthroughஅtheஅwildஅclover,அlaughterஅbubblingஅupஅfromஅhisஅchest.அClutchedஅinஅoneஅsmallஅhandஅwasஅaஅredஅrubberஅball,அscuffedஅandஅslightlyஅdeflated,அaஅloyalஅcompanionஅthroughஅcountlessஅbackyardஅadventures.அAtஅhisஅheelsஅboundedஅaஅfluffyஅpuppyஅnamedஅClover,அherஅearsஅfloppingஅwithஅeveryஅexuberantஅleap,அherஅyipsஅofஅexcitementஅpunctuatingஅtheஅwarmஅbreeze.அTheஅtwoஅmovedஅasஅone,அweavingஅthroughஅtheஅtallஅgrassஅlikeஅtwinஅcometsஅofஅjoy,அtheirஅworldஅaஅpatchworkஅofஅsunlight,அscent,அandஅmotion.அWithஅaஅdramaticஅflourish,அEliஅflungஅtheஅballஅhighஅintoஅtheஅair,அhisஅarmஅarcingஅlikeஅaஅslingshotஅreleased.அCloverஅshotஅforward,அherஅtinyஅlegsஅaஅblur,அchasingஅtheஅcrimsonஅblurஅasஅitஅsoared—until,அquiteஅunexpectedly,அtheஅballஅveeredஅmid-flightஅandஅdisappearedஅwithஅaஅsoftஅ*plop*அintoஅaஅnarrowஅholeஅhiddenஅamongஅtheஅrootsஅofஅanஅancientஅoak.அBothஅboyஅandஅdogஅskiddedஅtoஅaஅhalt,அblinkingஅatஅtheஅspotஅwhereஅtheஅballஅhadஅvanished.அCuriosityஅsparkingஅbrighterஅthanஅconcern,அEliஅdroppedஅtoஅhisஅkneesஅandஅpeeredஅintoஅtheஅhole,அexpectingஅmaybeஅaஅrabbitஅburrowஅorஅaஅhollowஅstump.அButஅwhatஅheஅsawஅinsteadஅmadeஅhisஅheartஅstutter—aஅfaint,அflickeringஅglow,அpulsingஅlikeஅaஅheartbeatஅfromஅdeepஅwithinஅtheஅearth.அCloverஅbarkedஅonce,அsharply,அthenஅsatஅdownஅwithஅherஅheadஅtilted,அasஅifஅwaitingஅforஅtheஅboyஅtoஅdecideஅwhatஅcameஅnext.அBreathஅcatchingஅinஅhisஅthroat,அEliஅreachedஅaஅtentativeஅhandஅtowardஅtheஅhole,அunawareஅthatஅinஅthatஅmoment,அheஅwasஅcrossingஅtheஅthresholdஅintoஅsomethingஅfarஅstrangerஅandஅmoreஅwondrousஅthanஅaஅgameஅofஅfetchஅcouldஅeverஅhaveஅpromised.நTheஅskyஅwasஅaஅvastஅexpanseஅofஅdeepeningஅblue,அstreakedஅwithஅtheஅgoldenஅhazeஅofஅtheஅsettingஅsun,அasஅTobyஅchasedஅhisஅlaughterஅacrossஅtheஅopenஅmeadow,அtheஅredஅballஅtuckedஅsnuglyஅunderஅoneஅarmஅlikeஅaஅsecretஅheஅwasஅdaringஅtheஅworldஅtoஅguess.அHisஅtousledஅhairஅcaughtஅtheஅlight,அglowingஅlikeஅburnishedஅcopper,அandஅbehindஅhimஅboundedஅaஅpuppyஅwithஅpawsஅtooஅbigஅforஅhisஅbody—Max,அaஅwhirlwindஅofஅfur,அfloppingஅears,அandஅpure,அunfilteredஅjoy.அTheyஅwereஅaஅblurஅofஅmotion,அboyஅandஅdog,அweavingஅthroughஅtallஅgrassஅandஅbuttercups,அtheஅballஅfinallyஅslippingஅfromஅToby’sஅgraspஅandஅbouncingஅahead,அbrightஅandஅboldஅagainstஅtheஅgreensஅandஅgolds.அMaxஅgaveஅaஅthrilledஅyipஅandஅlungedஅafterஅit,அbutஅjustஅasஅhisஅnoseஅbrushedஅtheஅball’sஅsurface,அtheஅgroundஅbeneathஅthemஅtrembled—notஅaஅgentleஅquake,அbutஅaஅsudden,அsharpஅjolt,அlikeஅtheஅearthஅitselfஅhadஅsneezed.அTheஅballஅbouncedஅonceஅmore,அthenஅstopped.அForஅaஅbreathlessஅsecond,அallஅwasஅstill.அThen,அwithஅaஅsoftஅ*crack*,அtheஅgroundஅsplitஅopenஅaஅfewஅfeetஅaway,அrevealingஅaஅjaggedஅholeஅrimmedஅwithஅglowingஅmossஅandஅwhisperingஅshadows.அTobyஅfroze,அhisஅheartbeatஅloudஅinஅhisஅears.அMaxஅgrowled—aஅlow,அconfusedஅrumble—asஅsomethingஅbeganஅtoஅriseஅfromஅtheஅgap:அaஅsmooth,அmetallicஅshape,அroundஅandஅblinkingஅwithஅtinyஅlights,அhummingஅfaintlyஅasஅitஅhoveredஅjustஅaboveஅtheஅgrass.அAஅdrone?அAஅtoy?அAஅtrickஅofஅtheஅlight?அNo—thisஅwasஅsomethingஅelseஅentirely.அTheஅairஅthickenedஅaroundஅthem,அchargedஅandஅhumming,அandஅsuddenlyஅtheஅredஅballஅliftedஅintoஅtheஅairஅonஅitsஅown,அslowlyஅspinning,அcaughtஅinஅanஅinvisibleஅforceஅthatஅtuggedஅatஅtheஅedgesஅofஅreality.அTobyஅreachedஅoutஅinstinctively,அbutஅMaxஅbarkedஅandஅlungedஅforward,அknockingஅhimஅbackஅjustஅasஅaஅbeamஅofஅsoftஅblueஅlightஅshotஅfromஅtheஅhoveringஅshapeஅtoஅwhereஅtheஅballஅhadஅbeen.அItஅvanished—*poof*—goneஅwithoutஅaஅsound.அTobyஅstared,அstunned,அtheஅechoஅofஅtheஅmomentஅvibratingஅinஅhisஅbones.அMaxஅlickedஅhisஅfaceஅanxiously,அtailஅwaggingஅinஅshort,அnervousஅbursts.அAndஅsomewhereஅbeneathஅtheஅsurfaceஅofஅtheஅearth,அtheஅholeஅsealedஅitselfஅagain,அleavingஅonlyஅtheஅcrushedஅgrassஅandஅaஅfaintஅscentஅofஅozoneஅbehind.அTheஅredஅball,அandஅwhateverஅhadஅclaimedஅit,அwasஅgone—butஅtheஅmeadowஅhadஅgrownஅquieter,அexpectant,அlikeஅitஅhadஅmoreஅsecretsஅyetஅtoஅtell.நTheஅsunஅhungஅlowஅoverஅtheஅhorizonஅlikeஅaஅsleepyஅeye,அcastingஅlongஅamberஅshadowsஅacrossஅtheஅcrackedஅsidewalkஅandஅtheஅovergrownஅedgesஅofஅtheஅvacantஅlotஅwhereஅJamieஅplayed,அhisஅredஅballஅclutchedஅtightஅinஅoneஅhandஅandஅhisஅotherஅarmஅflungஅwideஅasஅheஅran,அpretendingஅtoஅfly.அAtஅhisஅheelsஅtrailedஅBixby,அaஅfloppy-earedஅpuppyஅwithஅlegsஅtooஅlongஅforஅhisஅbody,அtrippingஅoverஅhisஅownஅpawsஅasஅheஅscrambledஅtoஅkeepஅup.அTheஅball—cherry-brightஅandஅscuffedஅfromஅcountlessஅgames—wasஅJamie’sஅmostஅprizedஅpossession,அtheஅcenterpieceஅofஅimaginaryஅworldsஅandஅbackyardஅtournaments,அaஅmagicalஅartifactஅoneஅday,அaஅplanetஅunderஅsiegeஅtheஅnext.அWithஅaஅsuddenஅwhoop,அJamieஅspunஅandஅhurledஅtheஅballஅintoஅtheஅair;அitஅsailedஅhigh,அcatchingஅtheஅlastஅraysஅofஅsunlightஅlikeஅaஅflare.அBixbyஅbarked,அeyesஅwide,அandஅchargedஅafterஅit,அhisஅtongueஅlollingஅandஅtailஅspinningஅlikeஅaஅpropeller.அButஅjustஅasஅtheஅballஅbeganஅitsஅdescent,அtheஅairஅaroundஅitஅshimmered—almostஅlikeஅheatஅwavesஅonஅasphalt—andஅthen,அinexplicably,அitஅvanished.அNotஅdropped,அnotஅcaught,அnotஅbouncedஅaway—vanished,அmid-air,அwithஅnoஅsoundஅorஅflash,அjustஅaஅstrange,அsuckingஅstillness.அJamieஅfroze,அblinking,அheartஅthuddingஅlikeஅaஅdrumline.அBixbyஅskiddedஅtoஅaஅconfusedஅhalt,அsniffingஅfuriouslyஅatஅtheஅpatchஅofஅemptyஅgroundஅwhereஅtheஅballஅshould’veஅlanded.அNoஅway,அJamieஅwhispered,அsteppingஅforwardஅcautiously,அhisஅeyesஅscanningஅtheஅairஅasஅthoughஅtheஅballஅmightஅreappearஅfromஅbehindஅsomeஅinvisibleஅcurtain.அThenஅcameஅaஅsoftஅhum,அbarelyஅaudible,அlikeஅtheஅwhirஅofஅdistantஅmachinery,அandஅfromஅtheஅspotஅwhereஅtheஅballஅhadஅdisappeared,அaஅflickerஅofஅlightஅspiraledஅupward—slow,அdeliberate,அandஅentirelyஅunnatural.அAsஅitஅclimbed,அitஅbeganஅtoஅshapeஅitselfஅintoஅsomething:அnotஅaஅsolidஅobject,அbutஅaஅfigure,அtallஅandஅflickering,அformedஅofஅthreadsஅofஅlightஅlikeஅneonஅmist.அJamieஅreachedஅforஅBixby,அwhoஅhadஅcrouchedஅlow,அgrowlingஅsoftlyஅnow,அfurஅbristlingஅwithஅinstinctiveஅunease.அTheஅfigureஅextendedஅaஅhand—orஅsomethingஅlikeஅone—towardஅJamie,அandஅinஅitsஅtranslucentஅpalm,அtheஅredஅballஅslowlyஅreappeared,அsuspendedஅinஅaஅshimmeringஅhalo.அJamieஅstared,அwide-eyed,அbreathஅheldஅtightஅinஅhisஅchest.அTheஅballஅfloatedஅthere,அofferedஅnotஅreturned,அlikeஅaஅgiftஅorஅmaybeஅaஅquestion,அasஅtheஅfigureஅwaitedஅinஅsilence,அitsஅformஅflickeringஅlikeஅcandlelightஅinஅaஅbreeze.அJamieஅdidn’tஅmove.அSomewhereஅinஅtheஅdistance,அaஅcarஅhornஅhonked,அaஅbirdஅcawed,அandஅtheஅworldஅbeyondஅtheஅvacantஅlotஅkeptஅspinning—obliviousஅtoஅtheஅboy,அtheஅdog,அandஅtheஅimpossibleஅmomentஅunfoldingஅlikeஅaஅdreamஅtooஅstrangeஅtoஅwakeஅfrom.நTheஅboy’sஅlaughterஅrangஅoutஅacrossஅtheஅsun-drenchedஅhillside,அhighஅandஅclearஅlikeஅtheஅnotesஅofஅaஅsongஅonlyஅheஅandஅtheஅwindஅknew.அHisஅnameஅwasஅJonah,அsevenஅyearsஅoldஅandஅwildஅasஅtheஅbreeze,அhisஅcheeksஅflushedஅfromஅtheஅthrillஅofஅtheஅchaseஅasஅheஅsprintedஅafterஅaஅbouncingஅredஅballஅthatஅshimmeredஅlikeஅaஅcherryஅinஅtheஅlateஅafternoonஅlight.அCloseஅbehindஅhimஅboundedஅaஅclumsyஅgoldenஅretrieverஅpuppyஅnamedஅScout,அherஅtailஅaஅjoyfulஅmetronomeஅkeepingஅtimeஅwithஅherஅawkward,அgallopingஅstrides.அTheஅhillஅwasஅsteep,அdottedஅwithஅbuttercupsஅandஅdandelionsஅthatஅburstஅintoஅtinyஅsunsஅwithஅeveryஅfootfall,அandஅtheஅtwoஅcompanions—boyஅandஅpup—racedஅdownwardஅinஅbreathlessஅpursuitஅofஅthatஅoneஅperfectஅthrow.அTheஅballஅtumbledஅandஅrolled,அfasterஅandஅfaster,அthenஅtookஅaஅsharpஅbounceஅoffஅaஅrootஅandஅlaunchedஅskyward,அsoaringஅinஅaஅbeautifulஅarcஅthatஅwouldஅhaveஅmadeஅJonahஅcheer,அifஅno