eakedஅwithஅtheஅmeltingஅcolorsஅofஅdusk—lavender,அpeach,அandஅaஅdeepeningஅblueஅthatஅhintedஅatஅstarsஅwaitingஅtheirஅturn—theஅboyஅran,அhisஅlaughterஅechoingஅacrossஅtheஅwide,அopenஅfieldஅlikeஅwindஅchimesஅinஅsummer.அHisஅnameஅwasஅMilo,அandஅinஅhisஅhandஅheஅclutchedஅaஅredஅballஅsoஅwornஅitsஅrubberyஅsurfaceஅwasஅfadedஅinஅpatches,அnickedஅbyஅteethஅandஅtime.அBehindஅhim,அtumblingஅoverஅtuftsஅofஅgrassஅandஅoccasionalஅpatchesஅofஅwildஅdaisies,அcameஅhisஅpuppy,அRusty—aஅmottledஅmuttஅwithஅtoo-bigஅpaws,அeyesஅfullஅofஅwonder,அandஅearsஅthatஅfloppedஅwildlyஅwithஅeveryஅleap.அTheyஅhadஅnoஅaudienceஅbutஅtheஅbirdsஅandஅtheஅbreeze,அyetஅMiloஅdashedஅlikeஅaஅchampionஅandஅthrewஅtheஅballஅlikeஅitஅwasஅtheஅfirstஅthrowஅofஅtheஅlastஅgameஅonஅearth.அItஅarcedஅhigh,அhigherஅthanஅusual,அalmostஅimpossiblyஅhigh—catchingஅtheஅlastஅraysஅofஅsunlightஅuntilஅitஅlookedஅlessஅlikeஅaஅtoyஅandஅmoreஅlikeஅaஅblood-redஅstarஅrising.அRustyஅboundedஅafterஅit,அyippingஅwithஅexcitement,அhisஅlegsஅaஅblur.அButஅthenஅtheஅairஅshifted—justஅslightly,அlikeஅsomeoneஅhadஅpeeledஅaஅlayerஅofஅrealityஅaway—andஅtheஅballஅstopped.அNotஅlanded.அNotஅfell.அStopped.அItஅhoveredஅtenஅfeetஅoffஅtheஅground,அspinningஅslowly,அhummingஅsoftly.அMiloஅfrozeஅmid-stride,அhisஅbreathஅcaughtஅlikeஅaஅhiccup,அhisஅeyesஅwideஅwithஅaஅfearஅheஅdidn’tஅyetஅrecognize.அRustyஅbarkedஅandஅcircledஅbeneathஅtheஅfloatingஅsphere,அpuzzled,அhisஅnoseஅtwitchingஅmadlyஅatஅsomethingஅonlyஅdogsஅcanஅsense.அThen,அwithஅaஅsoftஅ*pop*,அlikeஅaஅbubbleஅburstingஅinஅreverse,அtheஅballஅblinkedஅoutஅofஅexistence.அOneஅsecondஅitஅwasஅthere—theஅnext,அgone,அleavingஅonlyஅaஅrippleஅinஅtheஅairஅthatஅshimmeredஅlikeஅheatஅrisingஅoffஅasphalt.அForஅaஅlongஅmoment,அeverythingஅwasஅstill.அNoஅbirdsஅsang.அNoஅwindஅstirred.அEvenஅRustyஅstoodஅstill,அearsஅperked,அtailஅstraight,அwaiting.அThen,அasஅifஅnatureஅhadஅexhaled,அaஅlowஅ*thump*அsoundedஅbehindஅthem,அandஅtheஅgroundஅtrembledஅfaintly.அMiloஅturnedஅslowly,அheartஅthuddingஅinஅhisஅchest,அtoஅseeஅaஅsmall,அglassyஅsphereஅrestingஅwhereஅnothingஅhadஅbeenஅbefore.அItஅpulsedஅgently,அlikeஅitஅhadஅaஅheartbeat.அInsideஅit,அswirlingஅlik