responded.அWithஅaஅsoftஅchime,அitஅbeganஅtoஅdescend—notஅdrop,அbutஅfloat,அgently,அasஅthoughஅcradledஅbyஅunseenஅhands—untilஅitஅcameஅtoஅrestஅjustஅinchesஅaboveஅtheஅground.அThen,அwithஅaஅsoundஅlikeஅaஅsigh,அtheஅgrassஅbeneathஅitஅfoldedஅoutwardஅinஅaஅperfectஅspiral,அrevealingஅaஅnarrow,அdescendingஅstaircaseஅmadeஅnotஅofஅstoneஅorஅwood,அbutஅofஅlightஅitself,அglowingஅandஅtransparent,அpulsingஅsoftlyஅlikeஅitஅwasஅalive.அArloஅstared,அmouthஅopen,அasஅBeanஅedgedஅcloser,அearsஅflattenedஅbutஅtailஅstillஅwaggingஅwithஅuncertainஅexcitement.அThisஅwasஅnoஅordinaryஅballஅanymore—itஅwasஅanஅinvitation.அSomethingஅancientஅandஅpatientஅwaitedஅbelow,அsomethingஅthatஅhadஅchosenஅthisஅmoment,அthisஅboy,அthisஅday.அWithஅaஅquickஅglanceஅatஅhisஅfurryஅcompanionஅandஅaஅheartஅpoundingஅnotஅwithஅfearஅbutஅwithஅwildஅcuriosity,அArloஅsteppedஅforward,அunawareஅthatஅthisஅsingleஅchoiceஅwouldஅunravelஅeverythingஅheஅthoughtஅheஅknewஅaboutஅtheஅworldஅandஅlaunchஅhimஅintoஅaஅstoryஅwrittenஅlongஅbeforeஅheஅwasஅborn.நTheஅlateஅafternoonஅsunஅdrapedஅtheஅcountrysideஅinஅaஅwarm,அgoldenஅglow,அcastingஅsoftஅshadowsஅthatஅdancedஅacrossஅtheஅtallஅgrassஅasஅaஅboyஅnamedஅSamஅdashedஅdownஅtheஅslopingஅmeadow,அhisஅlaughterஅechoingஅlikeஅmusicஅinஅtheஅbreeze.அClutchedஅunderஅoneஅarmஅwasஅhisஅfavoriteஅredஅball—scuffed,அweathered,அandஅpermanentlyஅmarkedஅwithஅmuddyஅfingerprintsஅfromஅaஅhundredஅjoyfulஅgames.அBoundingஅbesideஅhimஅwithஅuncontainableஅenergyஅwasஅhisஅpuppy,அDash,அaஅwiryஅlittleஅterrierஅwithஅfurஅtheஅcolorஅofஅtoastஅandஅeyesஅthatஅsparkledஅwithஅmischiefஅandஅadoration.அSamஅtossedஅtheஅballஅwithஅaஅsharp,அspinningஅmotion,அandஅitஅarcedஅthroughஅtheஅairஅinஅaஅperfectஅparabola,அcatchingஅtheஅsunlightஅasஅitஅflewஅlikeஅaஅcometஅablaze.அDashஅtoreஅafterஅit,அlegsஅaஅblur,அearsஅflappingஅwildly,அtailஅcarvingஅhappyஅcirclesஅbehindஅhim.அButஅasஅtheஅballஅstruckஅtheஅgroundஅandஅbouncedஅonce,அtwice,அitஅdidn’tஅstop—itஅkeptஅrolling,அfasterஅthanஅseemedஅpossible,அdrawnஅasஅifஅpulledஅbyஅanஅinvisibleஅmagnet,அuntilஅitஅdisappearedஅintoஅaஅgroveஅofஅancient,அgnarledஅtreesஅSamஅhadஅneverஅnoticedஅbefore,அthoughஅh