n,அwithoutஅwarning,அsymbolsஅbeganஅtoஅbloomஅacrossஅitsஅsurface—alienஅandஅfluid,அlikeஅwritingஅmadeஅofஅwater—andஅtheஅballஅletஅoutஅaஅsoft,அmelodicஅchime.அBehindஅhim,அaஅlowஅgrowlஅrumbledஅfromஅtheஅunderbrush,அandஅEliஅturnedஅjustஅinஅtimeஅtoஅseeஅWhiskerஅstepஅbackஅintoஅview—butஅsomethingஅwasஅdifferent.அHisஅeyesஅglowedஅfaintly,அandஅheஅmovedஅwithஅeerieஅcalm,அlikeஅheஅwasn’tஅjustஅaஅpuppyஅanymoreஅbutஅaஅmessenger,அtouchedஅbyஅwhateverஅstrangeஅforceஅhadஅborrowedஅhim.அTheஅforestஅaroundஅthemஅhadஅgoneஅutterlyஅquiet.அEliஅlookedஅatஅtheஅhoveringஅball,அtheஅpulsingஅsymbols,அtheஅunnaturalஅcalmஅofஅhisஅonce-clumsyஅcompanion,அandஅknewஅinஅtheஅpitஅofஅhisஅstomachஅthatஅthisஅwasஅnoஅlongerஅjustஅaஅgameஅofஅfetch.அSomethingஅhadஅbegun—somethingஅancient,அsomethingஅwatching—andஅtheஅredஅballஅwasஅnotஅwhatஅitஅseemed.